  "title": "Slab-Built Wall Letter Sign in Air-Dry Clay",
  "subtitle": "A personalised clay letter or initial for the wall",
  "excerpt": "Cut a capital letter or initials from a flat slab of air-dry clay using a card template, pierce it for wall hanging, and seal with PVA once dry. No kiln needed and the whole project fits on a kitchen table.",
